  <body>

    <% include ../homepagetoolbar %>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h2>网格处理基础模块</h2>

        <h4>测试方法</h4>
        <p>这个模块的功能比较直观，可以直接参考<a href="/magic3d#meshshop" target="_blank">Magic3D</a>的使用说明进行功能测试。</p>

        <hr class="line-divider">
        <h4>功能展示</h4>

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="modulecaption">网格补洞</div>
            <ul class="moduleul">
            <li><div class="modulecontent">有四种补洞选项：三角化，平面，切向，曲率</div></li>
            <li><div class="modulecontent">可以处理凹边界的大洞</div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="/images/meshfillhole.jpg" alt="feature-modeling">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="line-divider">
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <img class="marginleft featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="/images/meshsimplification_small.jpg" alt="feature-modeling">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="modulecaption_right">网格简化</div>
            <ul class="moduleul_right">
            <li><div class="modulecontent">速度非常快</div></li>
            <li><div class="modulecontent">保持模型特征</div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="line-divider">
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="modulecaption">网格几何细节增强</div>
            <ul class="moduleul">
            <li><div class="modulecontent">增强网格的几何细节</div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="/images/MeshDetailEnhancement_small.jpg" alt="feature-modeling">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="line-divider">
        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <img class="marginleft featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="/images/meshdenoise.png" alt="feature-modeling">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="modulecaption_right">网格去噪</div>
            <ul class="moduleul_right">
            <li><div class="modulecontent">扫描的网格数据常常带有一些系统噪音，可以通过曲率查看 (如图第二排所示)</div></li>
            <li><div class="modulecontent">网格去噪不同于网格光顺，前者只去除掉噪音，而后者会光滑掉网格的几何细节</div></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="line-divider">
        <h3>如果您有任何疑问和建议，欢迎发email</h3>
        <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="/images/contact.jpg" alt="contact">

